    %% External flows
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>None/Bearer Token"| IstioGW
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Varies"| APIGW

    %% Ingress to service mesh
    IstioGW -->|"HTTP/80<br/>Istio mTLS"| KnAct
    APIGW -->|"HTTP/80<br/>Gateway-managed<br/>HTTPRoute rules"| Predictor

    %% Serverless flow
    KnAct -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (pod-local)"| Predictor

    %% LLM flow
    APIGW -->|"HTTP/80<br/>Gateway-managed"| InfPool
    InfPool -->|"HTTP/80<br/>mTLS/plaintext"| PrefillW
    InfPool -->|"HTTP/80<br/>mTLS/plaintext"| DecodeW

    %% Controller flows
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA token"| K8sAPI
    K8sAPI -->|"HTTPS/443->9443<br/>TLS cert-manager<br/>API server cert"| WebhookSvc
    KubeRBAC -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>pod-local"| Metrics

    %% Egress flows
    Predictor -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>IAM/Keys"| S3
    Predictor -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>GCS SA"| GCS
    Predictor -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Azure Creds"| Azure
    Predictor -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Registry Creds"| OCI
    Controller -->|"gRPC/4317<br/>plaintext"| KEDAOTel

